title: NFL ATL: Week 3 preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 3 preview
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling preview all the action coming up in Week 3 on top of a “Thursday Night Football” recap.  The crew also defends its hero picks and taunts Wesseling about eating his softball pants. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL and #NFLATL.
